NAF.raw: http : / / www . cbs8 . com / story / 10120887 / city - attorney - weighs - filing - dui - charges - against - chargers - jamal - williams ? redirected=true City Attorney Weighs Filing DUI Charges Against Chargers' Jamal Williams Posted : Apr 02 , 2009 11 : 06 PM CEST Updated : Apr 02 , 2009 11 : 06 PM CEST The City Attorney's Office was considering today whether to file misdemeanor drunken - driving charges against Chargers defensive lineman Jamal Williams . Williams , 32 , was arrested around 1 : 30 a . m . Feb . 1 on state Route 94 on suspicion of drunken driving . Results from a blood - alcohol test administered when Williams was arrested were released Wednesday , showing a level of 0 . 07 percent - - just under the state legal limit of 0 . 08 percent , California Highway Patrol Officer Brian Pennings told The San Diego Union - Tribune . He said the blood was drawn well after Williams' arrest , meaning he could have been intoxicated when when officers pulled him over for speeding in his 2008 Bentley . City Attorney spokeswoman Gina Coburn told the Union - Tribune the case remains under review and is being investigated further .
